Heh, I agree.  I'm 45, and there's a room with those fairies, and necyomancers.  Two 28 Spec nukes, let a level 45 Experienced Necyo finish up, move on to the next.  Once the room's cleared, rest for pop.  I get emeralds easily enough.<P>There's also a place on the way down to the Cooks.  I've only been there once, but all the mobs conned Blue to me, and they dropped Sapphires.  Now that's pretty good too, as Sapphires work for those who want better than emerald, but can't afford the covetted Diamonds.
